{"tid":362333,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[起底組]港婦台北怒打捷運保安","createTime":"2017-08-16T23:48:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-17T02:59:21.000Z","uid":73883,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bf821792a20527e15afd0921240ad36105e61898","tid":362333,"uid":73883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T23:48:31.000Z","msg":"搭機捷帶超長釣竿遭阻　港籍悍婦怒捶保全<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n機場捷運台北A1台北站，今天上午9時許，四名香港籍遊客準備進站搭車時，因其中一名男子手上握的釣竿目測超過200公分，但機捷規定物品長度不能超過160公分，於是保全上前表示攜帶過長的釣竿無法搭乘，沒想到港男妻子竟一把奪走釣竿，保全阻攔反遭港女痛毆胸口三拳，經勸說後由母親帶著兩女搭車，父親則拿著釣竿獨自離開捷運站。<br />\n<br />\n機捷表示，兩名香港籍夫妻帶著兩名小孩，準備從機場捷運台北A1台北站搭車前往一航廈，因手上釣竿過長遭阻，沒想到妻子一把搶走釣竿便往直達車月台狂奔，遭樓下保全阻擋後，更往保全胸口毆打，後來遭桃園捷運警察隊制止，保全因無大礙不願提告。"},{"pid":"dedbc5c948f1ee3a1efeb5f41249726e419d5e3f","tid":362333,"uid":73883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T23:50:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170816/1183547/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fnew%2F20170816%2F1183547%2F&d=FFjObML1d9G%2FX%2BfIzmeofwdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=1fccb68a\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170816/1183547/</a>"},{"pid":"d91e527f8c8c358728d49466c10653de57bc7832","tid":362333,"uid":40779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T23:51:54.000Z","msg":"支那基因"},{"pid":"2340dc67b32a019845577f38450c92d327cbe0d3","tid":362333,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T23:54:10.000Z","msg":"咁都唔告個八婆?<br />\n唯有網球公審條臭閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d03ebfd6fe12ac2025fb8af151b7c163f90d2201","tid":362333,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T23:54:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁都唔告個八婆?<br />\n唯有網絡公審條臭閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"3f23cedd371a3724e7a8a6a7a4bd3e8e4274b32c","tid":36233